# AI Engineering Connection

Hash-based lookups are widely used in AI systems:

- LLM response caching
- Embedding caches
- Feature stores
- Prompt lookup tables

Understanding HashMap internals helps explain why these systems can retrieve previously computed results in near O(1) time.